The flat, with 490 sqft super area and 435 sqft carpet area, is located in one of the desirable locations of Rani Sati Nagar, Nadiyawala Colony 1, Mumbai. Property Specifications With an east-facing entrance, this apartment is designed in line with Vaastu principles to promote a happy and healthy existence. Bright and airy, this property positioned on the top floor of a 4-storey building is well-built and ideal to provide a comfortable life to a nuclear family.Moving on, the flat features an SV road (west) facing bedroom, common bathroom, a garden-facing living room and kitchen. The apartment comes with good sized rooms and is mindfully furnished with a sofa, 1 TV, fridge, 2 wardrobes, a bed and an AC. Designed in Indian style, the bathroom is fitted with high-end fixtures and a geyser to provide a hot water supply 24x7. There is enough room in the kitchen for comfortable cooking whereas the flooring of all the rooms is covered with mosaic tiles to give the interiors a clean finish. Furthermore, you can simply customise the rooms of this home to suit your requirements and preferences.Facilities Besides this, the residential apartment has access to basic facilities like round a clock water supply, 100% power backup and open parking. Security is maintained round the clock via guards and CCTV monitoring.Locality The apartment is 10min from the Western Express Highway and is part of a well-planned society housing 175 flats that are located on the main SV road. Hence, this apartment enjoys good connectivity to various parts of the city. Within 5 seconds, you can have access to vegetables, fruits, milk, grocery and other kinds of shops. There are 3 famous schools as well as multiple gardens and temples in the vicinity. Inorbit Mall and Infinity Mall are hardly within 10min reach of the apartment. The railway station is 7-8min walking distance from the apartment and other public transports are widely available in this area.
